---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  lang="en"
  title="Privacy Policy | GymAI Club"
  description="GymAI Club privacy policy."
>
  <Nav lang="en" />
  <main class="info-page wrap">
    <section class="info-hero">
      <div class="sec-kicker">PRIVACY POLICY</div>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p></p>
    </section>

    <section class="info-card legal" aria-label="Privacy policy content area">
      <div class="legal-updated">Last Updated: July 6, 2026</div>

      <p>At GymAI Club ("the App"), we care about your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains what data we collect while you use the App, how we use that data, and what rights you have.</p>

      <h2>1. Data Controller</h2>
      <p>This App is developed and operated by the individual developer <strong>Onur Küçüktürk</strong>. For privacy-related questions, you can reach us at <a href="mailto:gymaiclub01@gmail.com">gymaiclub01@gmail.com</a>.</p>

      <h2>2. Data We Collect</h2>

      <h3>2.1 Account Information</h3>
      <p>When you sign in through your Google or Apple account, we receive basic identity information (name, email address, profile photo). This information is used solely to create your account and verify your identity.</p>

      <h3>2.2 Camera Data</h3>
      <p>The App requests access to your device's camera in order to analyze your exercise form. This analysis is performed <strong>entirely on your device (on-device)</strong>; your camera footage is never transmitted to or stored on our servers.</p>

      <h3>2.3 Photo Gallery</h3>
      <p>Access to your photo gallery is requested so you can choose a profile picture. The photo you select is used only to be displayed on your profile.</p>

      <h3>2.4 Health and Fitness Data (Apple HealthKit)</h3>
      <p>If you grant permission, your workout progress and daily activity may be shared with the Apple Health app. This data is used solely to provide you with a personalized workout experience; it is not used for advertising or marketing purposes and is not shared with third parties.</p>

      <h3>2.5 AI-Powered Features</h3>
      <p>The App uses a recommendation logic based on your goal, fitness level, and workout frequency to generate personalized workout plans. This process is performed entirely within the App; your data is not transmitted to a third-party AI service for this purpose.</p>

      <h3>2.6 Usage Data</h3>
      <p>Basic technical data (device model, operating system version, app version, crash reports) may be collected to ensure the App functions properly.</p>

      <h2>3. Data We Do Not Use</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>We do not use any advertising or tracking SDKs</strong> (such as the Facebook SDK or AdMob).</li>
        <li>We do not collect or use your device's Advertising Identifier.</li>
        <li>We do not collect your location data.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. Sharing of Data</h2>
      <p>Your personal data is not shared with third parties except in the following cases:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Where required by a legal obligation</li>
        <li>With subprocessors that are essential to providing the service (such as cloud infrastructure providers), limited strictly to operating the service</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>5. Data Security</h2>
      <p>Your data is protected with industry-standard security measures (encrypted connections - HTTPS). However, we remind you that no transmission over the internet is 100% secure.</p>

      <h2>6. Data Retention and Deletion</h2>
      <p>You can permanently delete your account at any time through <strong>Settings → Delete Account</strong> within the App. When your account is deleted, your associated personal data is removed from our systems.</p>

      <h2>7. Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>The App is not directed at individuals under the age of 18. We do not knowingly collect data from users we know to be under 18 years old.</p>

      <h2>8. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>Regarding your personal data, you have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Request access to your data</li>
        <li>Request correction of your data</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
      </ul>
      <p>You can submit these requests to <a href="mailto:gymaiclub01@gmail.com">gymaiclub01@gmail.com</a>.</p>

      <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. If significant changes are made, we will notify you within the App.</p>

      <h2>10. Contact</h2>
      <p>For questions about this Privacy Policy: <strong><a href="mailto:gymaiclub01@gmail.com">gymaiclub01@gmail.com</a></strong></p>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer lang="en" />
</BaseLayout>
